description: Sets a configuration set's default for message feedback.

parameters.name: ConfigurationSetName
parameters.description: The name of the configuration set to use. This can be either the ConfigurationSetName or ConfigurationSetArn.

parameters.name: MessageFeedbackEnabled
parameters.description: Set to true to enable message feedback.

nested_items.description: The arn of the configuration set.

nested_items.description: True if message feedback is enabled.
